## Gotchas
- HubSpot v1 engagements/paged API is deprecated — may return stale data
- `GET /api/hubspot/sync` (full contact/company/deal sync) does INSERT OR REPLACE → resets engagement_score to NULL — MUST run `POST /api/hubspot/enrich-contacts` after every sync
- scheduled() cron only syncs threads — contacts/companies/deals caches go stale without manual trigger
- Thread dedup: normalize subjects (strip Re:/Fwd:, lowercase, trim) before MD5 hashing
- Recipients with typos (e.g. mcgillidray vs mcgillivray) create duplicate threads — deduplicate by normalized subject + contact within 24h window
- involves_luis uses integer (0/1) in D1 — frontend must parseInt() for comparison
- Internal domains: clearskyltd.com, leadingcarbon.com, maboroshi.com
